         <ttm:title>American Recovery and Reinvestment Act (ARRA)</ttm:title>
         <ttm:desc>The American Recovery and Reinvestment Act (ARRA) Modification allows Contractors to change whether they would like to opt in or opt out of the Program. Opting in allows Contractors to accept Orders made with Recovery Act funds.
         </ttm:desc>
