   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:02.03" end="00:00:04.56" region="speaker">This screen allows you to modify your response to</p>
         <p begin="00:00:04.56" end="00:00:08.56" region="speaker">the American Recovery And Reinvestment Act of 2009.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:08.56" end="00:00:10.83" region="speaker">By participating in the program, you are allowed</p>
         <p begin="00:00:10.83" end="00:00:13.80" region="speaker">to accept orders made with recovery act funds.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:13.80" end="00:00:16.70" region="speaker">You will see a question asking whether or not your</p>
         <p begin="00:00:16.70" end="00:00:19.20" region="speaker">company accepts all clauses associated with</p>
         <p begin="00:00:19.20" end="00:00:22.40" region="speaker">the American Recovery and Reinvestment Act.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:22.40" end="00:00:24.53" region="speaker">Participating in the program allows you to</p>
         <p begin="00:00:24.53" end="00:00:26.90" region="speaker">accept orders that are made with recovery act</p>
         <p begin="00:00:26.90" end="00:00:28.16" region="speaker">funds.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:28.16" end="00:00:29.96" region="speaker">Choose Yes or No.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:29.96" end="00:00:32.50" region="speaker">When you finish, click &quot;Save and Continue.&quot;</p>
    </div>
